text: John Payn (fl. 1391) of Swaffham Prior, Cambridgeshire, was an English politician, lawyer and landowner. He was a Member (MP) of the Parliament of England for Cambridge in 1391. ==References== Category:Year of birth missing Category:Year of death missing Category:English MPs 1391 Category:14th-century English lawyers Category:People from East Cambridgeshire District
